                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xl-4">
                    <h3 class="text-center">СВЯЖИТЕСЬ С НАМИ</h3>
                    <hr class="border-white w-50" />
                    <div class="icon-bar">
                        <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>
